fix.fixtext:
Configure proper file permissions:
1. Set library permissions: chmod 644 /usr/local/lib/libwolfssl.so* 2. Set library permissions: chmod 644 /usr/local/lib/libwolfprov.so* 3. Set config permissions: chmod 644 /etc/ssl/openssl.cnf 4. Set script permissions: chmod 755 /scripts/*.sh 5. Remove world-writable: find / -type f -perm -002 -exec chmod o-w {} \;
Rebuild container with proper file permissions.
